reviewText: The same issue as with the previous course within this professional certification. You really need to work on the preparation and concept for this course. Absolute failure in learning psychology. I'm just struggling through these uninspiring, boring, monotonous videos as I'd like to acquire the certificate. Totally interesting topics but the way the teachers are presenting it makes me fall asleep after two sentences. Basically talking heads reading the pre-written text - without any visual clues, seeming to be bored themselves. The reason that there are two stars here is that the content is actually interesting and relevant you just need not to fall asleep during the lectures

Documentation was pretty good, but the practical part I have received many documents to review which are empty or do not have content. Who can I ask when I have question about the "logistics" of the course? Thanks!
